# Apps Directory â€“ RockstarHQ Monorepo

This `/apps` folder contains all major apps, SaaS tools, and micro-frontends for Rockstar Barnum & Co.

## Structure

- **rockstarbarnum/**  
  The main landing site for [rockstarbarnum.com](https://rockstarbarnum.com).

- **barnumsstudio/**  
  The SaaS dashboard, AI tools, and subscription services (for [barnumsstudio.online](https://barnumsstudio.online)).

- **preservation-monitor/**  
  Preservation STARZ and heritage monitoring tools (optional: add as needed).

- **phoenecia/**  
  Phoenecia Online app or directory platform.

## Getting Started

Each app should be a standalone Next.js or React project.  
To add a new app, simply create a new subfolder here and scaffold your project (e.g., `npx create-next-app@latest`).

